data.description: Welcome to your charming haven nestled just minutes away from the convenience of Highway 20 and Buford Dam Rd. This adorable 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom craftsman-style home is a perfect blend of comfort and style.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living room, perfect for cozy evenings or entertaining guests. The open kitchen boasts a breakfast area, pantry, and a convenient laundry room nearby. French doors beckon you into the separate dining room, offering versatility as an office space or playroom, ensuring every inch of this home is utilized to its fullest potential.    Upstairs, indulge in the luxury of an oversized master bedroom, complete with not one, not two, but three walk-in closets to accommodate all your storage needs effortlessly.    One of the unique highlights of this property is its private, fenced-in backyard, providing a serene retreat that backs up to 10 acres of lush green space, where you can enjoy the beauty of nature and catch glimpses of wildlife in their natural habitat.    Noteworthy is the recent addition of a new HVAC unit, updated lighting fixtures, new Nest Thermostats, new flooring, new interior paint, new fence in the back yard, new SOD and a roof that is only three years old, ensuring peace of mind and longevity for years to come.    Experience the sense of community that this neighborhood offers while enjoying the convenience of being less than a half mile from Gary Pirkle Park boasting a covered playground, soccer fields, and scenic walking trails for outdoor enthusiasts of all ages, less than a half mile to the Sugar Hill Community Garden, 5 minutes to shopping, dining and schools.    With its move-in ready condition and unbeatable location, this home is a rare find that promises a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and endless possibilities.
